# 🛑 OMNICLAW ACADEMY - ARTIFACT HYGIENE
# This file enforces the 8th Pillar: Artifact Publishing Security.
# Prevents accidental leakages of Source Maps, Configs, and Contexts during releases.

# Source maps expose internal system architectures to attackers
*.map

# Credentials and Local Configurations
*.env
*.env.*
.env*
.env.example
*.pem
*.key
credentials.json
openclaw.json
claude.json
gemini.json

# OmniClaw Brain & Logs
brain/
storage/vault/quarantine/
telemetry/
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# Mac & Windows OS Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# Agent Contexts
.gemini/
.claude/
.cursor/
.history/
.nullclaw/
.vscode/

# Local Dev
node_modules/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
